com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.inventory

Class ManagedObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.ExtensibleObject
      • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.inventory.ManagedObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Binary

    public class ManagedObject
extends ExtensibleObject
    Represents a ManagedObject from the platform.

    The ManagedObject can model any physical or cyber-physical object, even virtual object.

    Created by Patrick Steinert on 30.01.16.
